featured_reviews.review_id:
Nice place to visit. Its a unique building made during the time of Ruler Ahmad. You can also visit the grave of mothet of Ruler Ahmad.

The building has unique and intricate carvings and is built from stones. The mosque has lot of pillars which supports the entire structure.

The mosque is declared as a heritage building but is not very well maintained as compared to other monuments.

The Government must take care of this beautiful monument
